info.description: Da ShAmAn's first wii old skool demo
info.details:
Da ShAmAn is back with a shout out to talented ppl who want to form a team for wii brew creations, can you make rockin trax or cool lookin logos and fonts ? then get in touch - hint search the binary for .com

Well here we are again... 20 odd years down the line and boy does the internet make demo coding and homebrew a whole world (sorry) easier  .......... greetz fly out to  lynnie, debbie, daimo, paxo, anastasiya and beppie, andreas, lara
